com.cmput301.t05.habilect

Class AddHabitEventDialogInformationGetter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301.t05.habilect.AddHabitEventDialogInformationGetter

  • public class AddHabitEventDialogInformationGetter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to facilitate getting information from an addHabitEventDialog. It should be passed the resultBundle from the dialog when making the class. Then simply call the methods you want to get the information you need.
